N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 174.6 - Special event stickers

State Regulations

The commissioner, upon request, may approve windshield
stickers for use at special events for limited periods. Stickers must be
removed at the conclusion of the event. Notes
